prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, pop art comic book style, featuring an action-packed, humorous scene on a snowy mountain peak under a bright blue sky. A cartoon illustrated version of Lao Lao from the photo is mid-air on a snowboard, expertly grabbing the edge of her board with a huge, joyful smile. A cartoon version of Jordan from the photo is comically half-buried head-first in a pile of snow at the bottom of a small jump, his snowboard sticking up in the air. A pack of three adorable, cartoonishly enthusiastic dogs (a Golden Retriever, a Husky, and a small Corgi) are wearing tiny goggles and bandanas, cheering from the sidelines and kicking up snow. The entire scene is framed with dynamic action lines and a vibrant sunburst pattern in the background. In the center of the card, a large, yellow comic book-style speech bubble contains the words "Happy Birthday, My Superhero!" in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The artwork is flat 2D with bold outlines, halftone dot patterns for shading, and a bright, saturated color palette of cyan, magenta, and yellow.
